{"tid":1839544,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊受成預告幫阿嬌婚宴埋單","createTime":"2020-01-24T13:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T13:05:40.000Z","uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"402db55edcdd8dfa7335e0cf5e9ee8c6642037c0","tid":1839544,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"2018-11-25<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181125/large/c0305a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181125%2Flarge%2Fc0305a.gif&h=13195244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">楊受成前晚出席活動時預告會包辦阿嬌（小圖）婚宴的酒席開支。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n英皇老闆楊受成、周焯華（洗米華）、吳浩康和彭秀慧等，前晚在銅鑼灣出席電影《箭神．第一戰》首映，洗米華雖未有接受訪問，但他在現場卻跟楊受成不停密斟。<br />\n<br />\n鍾欣潼（阿嬌）下月20日便結婚，問到楊受成可要阿嬌跪地斟茶？他答：「要斟茶，但唔使跪啦。」楊受成答應包辦酒席和酒水：「唔知幾多圍，酒店嗰度最多40幾圍，應該都會擺晒。」楊受成表示未知埋單多少錢，但都會有上限。屆時會上台致賀辭嗎？楊受成說：「唔講啦，咁老土，驚講講吓我會喊。」至於會否催阿嬌快啲生仔？楊生話：「我點催到，我個仔都催唔到，順其自然啦。」<br />\n採訪、攝影：羅慧敏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20181125/20553947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181125%2F20553947&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77YE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=35d4a714\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181125%2F20553947&h=10291c90\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20181125/20553947</a>"},{"pid":"99a6bb32f309099971a5639168a420938ad69a93","tid":1839544,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"真正嘅埋單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2224756/org/47606137bd1268f6f964cfbd3070476f.jpg/3da4i553vSj3zp-mFQ8fg-76htsrmF2TYMvnSmDL50o?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht